OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely dry day with bright
OL,6,Fspells. Cloud will thicken at times in
OL,7,Fthe west to bring the odd spot of
OL,8,Frain. Remaining warm, especially in
OL,9,Fthe east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be a rather cloudy
OL,12,Fevening but some brightness in places.
OL,13,FRemaining dry overnight with
OL,14,Flengthening clear spells. A mild night.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FA largely dry day with plenty
OL,17,Fof sunshine and feeling warm. Cloudier
OL,18,Fwith a little rain early in the
OL,19,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
