OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fand bright with plenty of sunshine
OL,7,Fduring this period. Becoming
OL,8,Fincreasingly warm in general, but
OL,9,Fcooler at times along the east coast.
